        <abstract>
            <p>CD partly right. JDH was calling "stratification" what CD calls "foliation". Answers CD’s question on cleavage foliation in Himalayas. Glacial action.</p> 
<p>Charmed by CD’s Admiralty instructions on geology [in <hi rend="italic">Manual of scientific enquiry</hi> (1849), <hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 1: 227–50], but complains he does not give prices of books and instruments he recommends.</p> 
        </abstract>
